                     <interp inst="t18741214-77-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">The Jury stated that they did not believe Clarks evidence.</hi> 
